- Change project name in "CMakeLists.txt"
- Don't change executable name in "CMakeLists.txt"
- Save source code in "src/"
- Go to "workspace/" then execute:
	+ [build.sh]		: clean "build/" then build
	+ [exec.sh] 		: execute the program
	+ [build_exec.sh]	: clean, build, remove makefiles in build then execute
	+ [clean.sh]		: clean "build/" (remove all files)
	+ [clean_makefiles.sh]	: clean "build/" (remove makefiles only)
	
